data.Name: Nothing Left
data.Bio: 1) Old school hardcore band from Plovdiv, Bulgaria. 2) We're 5 guys, playing metalcore, headbanging, moshing, working, eating, sleeping,drinking, fucking, ducking, trucking, packing, whatever ing... just listen! :-* 3) Wilkes-Barre hardcore 4) Nothing Left burn down the house with their gritty, two fisted approach to hardcore. Raw and angry, this 6-song EP refuels the flames of the early hardcore movement and makes you remember the dynamic underground music scene of your youth. Read more on Last.fm
